title: Talks Machina: Discussing C1E95 and C1E96 - One Year Later / Family Matters
description: Brian Wayne Foster is your host for Talks Machina! He's joined by Ashley Johnson, Travis Willingham, and Laura Bailey to discuss Critical Role episodes 95 and 96, give out fan art and GIF of the week prizes, and answer questions!
